transArray.content: Very close to the test center. The front desk service attitude is very good. The room is clean and hygienic and the sound insulation effect is good.

Snowflake has a pure and peaceful world. In the world of rain, we have a kind of freshness and warmth. In our world, from your words, we feel the tenderness of water, the warmth of the sunset, and a beautiful emotion. Dear student, I wish you always face the warm breeze blowing on your face and the singing of birds and the fragrance of flowers. Love your Hanting
